Welcome to the APlus Hurricane Explorer!

You can drag this model into your document to run your own storm models. The Storm Explorer model shown here has high pressure systems that drive the storm out to sea. It never gets to be more than a tropical storm. If you want to rerun this model drag the model into your workspace on the right.
